data.description: Why Wait For New Construction! Welcome Home to 165 Lindera Preserve Blvd. This popular Jasper Model sits on a premium Pond lot. As you enter the home you will be impressed with the high ceilings and impressive foyer. There is a guest bedroom on the first floor with a full bathroom. The formal dining room is perfect for holiday gatherings. The two story living room steps out to an easy breeze all season porch to enjoy year round. The gourmet kitchen is a cooks delight with an oversized island, stainless steel appliances, double wall ovens with convection oven on top, 36'' gas cooktop and vented microwave. The kitchen opens to the family room making this space perfect for entertaining. The Butlers Pantry is tucked away behind the kitchen with abundant storage and convenient work/tech stationThe large master bedroom, which has its own HVAC zone, is located upstairs and overlooks the picturesque pond. The master closets both have custom closet systems. The large master bathroom with tile flooring includes dual vanities, soaking tub, separate shower, water closet and linen closet.  Storage is not an issue in this home. The 2 additional bedrooms upstairs also have custom closet systems and are both generous size with full bathroom in between the bedrooms. The large bonus room located upstairs can be a flex room or media room. The laundry room is also conveniently located upstairs. The home includes an irrigation system and gutter system.
